134
00:07:51,968 --> 00:07:53,344
Oh, Tuhan.

135
00:08:03,008 --> 00:08:05,887
Mari kita cari cara untuk
mendapatkan anakmu kembali.

136
00:08:05,888 --> 00:08:08,575
Siapa kau?

137
00:08:08,576 --> 00:08:11,167
Aku di sini untuk menolongmu.

138
00:08:11,168 --> 00:08:12,607
Di mana Sam?

139
00:08:12,608 --> 00:08:14,719
Di mana anakku?

140
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:16,414
Kau bersama penculiknya, bukan?

141
00:08:16,415 --> 00:08:17,408
Kau salah satu dari mereka..

142
00:08:17,409 --> 00:08:19,999
